21:18.242 --> 21:25.710
And there's something that happens when I look at all that pile of bills and I can't sleep, I'm sweating, and I begin to pray, am I quite time?

21:25.750 --> 21:33.377
God, you said, Philippians 4 verse 19, that you would supply all of my need according to your riches and glory.

21:35.680 --> 21:37.742
