21:38.242 --> 21:39.584
I thank you Lord, that you're doing that.

21:39.604 --> 21:40.985
You're supplying all of my needs.

21:41.245 --> 21:42.086
You have it, God.

21:42.106 --> 21:42.927
It's under control.

21:42.987 --> 21:44.349
I don't got to worry about it.

21:44.369 --> 21:45.810
God, you're working it all out.

21:47.394 --> 21:49.156
Maybe you feel like you're not good enough.

21:49.716 --> 21:51.899
