21:51.959 --> 21:55.182
You say, Colossians two, verse 10.

21:55.963 --> 22:00.448
God, you said that I'm complete in you who is the head of all principality and power.

22:00.928 --> 22:07.755
God, I thank you that every place that I'm lacking in my personality, in my education and Holy Spirit, you're making up for it.

22:07.875 --> 22:08.936
You're taking care of it.

22:09.677 --> 22:13.401
And as I begin to meditate and pray God's word back to him, guess what?

22:13.421 --> 22:14.482
I have great peace.

22:14.658 --> 22:17.202
Peace comes Psalms 119 verse 165.

22:17.562 --> 22:19.865
Great peace have those who love your law.

22:21.247 --> 22:23.971
The next one, number three, is request.

22:24.232 --> 22:25.794
We just talked about that Philippians 4.

22:26.134 --> 22:29.700
Request, bring your needs to God and ask Him for help.

22:30.481 --> 22:33.825
It's amazing how many Christians today, they just don't do that.

22:35.067 --> 22:36.069
They just don't do that.

22:36.129 --> 22:38.472
They think they could take care of it all on their own.

22:38.492 --> 22:39.794
They carry that burden.

22:40.802 --> 22:45.529
They whine about it, they gripe about it, they complain about it, and God's saying, I'm here to help you.

22:46.330 --> 22:49.475
And let me tell you, when you make that request, guess what?

22:49.615 --> 22:50.877
Anxiety begins to leave.

22:51.638 --> 22:52.840
Fear begins to go.

22:53.601 --> 22:55.844
Number five, tongues.

22:57.587 --> 23:04.918
You know the Bible says in 1 Corinthians 14 that you and I, we pray mysteries when we use our prayer language.

23:04.938 --> 23:07.762
As you know, the Bible says that when you and I pray in tongues,

23:07.938 --> 23:10.662
that we're actually praying the perfect will of God.

23:10.682 --> 23:14.147
Do you have something in your life that you just don't know the answer for?

23:14.608 --> 23:16.871
You got no clue how God's gonna fix it.

23:17.151 --> 23:23.320
In fact, you don't, I mean, you don't have an ankle, you've gone to the Bible to try to find a verse regarding God's will in this situation.

23:23.600 --> 23:24.321
You can't find it.

23:24.482 --> 23:25.423
Guess what you need to do?

23:26.204 --> 23:27.105
You have praying tongues.

23:28.287 --> 23:32.994
The Bible says that we pray in the tongue of a man or an angel and we're praying God's perfect will.

23:33.114 --> 23:36.018
As we begin to do that, let me tell you, 10 minutes,

