25:19.723 --> 25:29.778
A few years ago, and the team could come now, but a few years ago, actually around 2016, we took a family hiking trip to

25:29.986 --> 25:34.712
this place in the desert near Arizona is called the Mecha Wilderness.

25:35.593 --> 25:37.896
