25:37.916 --> 25:42.041
It's about 40 square miles of all these kind of rolling desert hills.

25:42.381 --> 25:46.787
There's like these kind of crevices and gullies and little canyons and that type of thing.

25:47.347 --> 25:50.711
And I was gonna take our kids hiking.

25:50.732 --> 25:52.474
It was me, Dad, Steven, Tamara.

25:53.215 --> 25:57.260
And my littlest one, Lana, it was her first time hiking.

25:57.940 --> 25:59.282
