27:02.613 --> 27:06.800
So we walked another little ways and she starts complaining so hot.

27:07.762 --> 27:10.207
Oh, she would just sit back act like she was dying.

27:11.469 --> 27:13.192
We're seriously, we're not that far along.

27:13.252 --> 27:16.338
I mean, we haven't even gone a quarter of a mile and she's

27:16.930 --> 27:17.831
She's griping.

27:17.891 --> 27:18.932
