27:27.020 --> 27:27.881
Again, I go to her.

27:27.901 --> 27:29.103
Lana, can I pick you up?

27:29.203 --> 27:29.983
Can I carry you?

27:31.125 --> 27:32.746
Your father loves you.

27:34.468 --> 27:36.871
