28:14.626 --> 28:22.579
Not only did I take her trouble, not only did I take her anxiety, all that, I gave her the strength to make it the rest of the journey.

28:24.843 --> 28:28.549
I have some pictures I want to show you because you can see, she was having fun.

28:30.552 --> 28:32.976
