29:13.796 --> 29:17.101
But so many of us, we got pride.

29:17.843 --> 29:18.804
Maybe it's ignorance.

29:19.886 --> 29:25.154
Maybe it's just, we think we can do a better job or some, we want to get the answer from someplace else.

29:26.336 --> 29:27.478
God's saying, no, come to me.

29:28.640 --> 29:32.206
Come to me all year, heavy laden, and I will give you rest.

29:33.488 --> 29:34.930
