30:41.736 --> 30:42.197
Thank you.

30:42.718 --> 30:43.478
Raise your hand high.

30:43.578 --> 30:44.239
Don't be ashamed.

30:44.339 --> 30:44.760
Thank you.

30:45.901 --> 30:46.302
Thank you.

